{
  "video_id": "0VIaL7lbgv4",
  "title": "Crime and Outrage",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 640.0,
      "text": "Good morning Hank. It's Tuesday."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 640.0,
      "end_time": 1400.0,
      "text": "I want to ask you a question."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 1400.0,
      "end_time": 3480.0,
      "text": "Do you think the violent crime rate in the United States"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 3480.0,
      "end_time": 5540.0,
      "text": "has gone up or down"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 5540.0,
      "end_time": 7000.0,
      "text": "or stayed about the same"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 7000.0,
      "end_time": 8000.0,
      "text": "since 1990?"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 8000.0,
      "end_time": 11140.0,
      "text": "The answer is, that it has gone down, dramatically!"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 11140.0,
      "end_time": 13580.0,
      "text": "In fact, there are about half as many violent crimes"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 13580.0,
      "end_time": 15000.0,
      "text": "per one thousand Americans"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 15000.0,
      "end_time": 16700.0,
      "text": "as there were 25 years ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 16700.0,
      "end_time": 18700.0,
      "text": "Overall, crime rates are also down dramatically"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 18700.0,
      "end_time": 20700.0,
      "text": "but every year since 2006"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 20700.0,
      "end_time": 23360.0,
      "text": "at least 60 percent of Americans polled"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 23360.0,
      "end_time": 24660.0,
      "text": "have said that they feel that"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 24660.0,
      "end_time": 25860.0,
      "text": "\"crime is going up\"."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 25860.0,
      "end_time": 27120.0,
      "text": "And I am among them. In fact, I wanted"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 27120.0,
      "end_time": 29180.0,
      "text": "to make a video about why crime is going up"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 29180.0,
      "end_time": 30800.0,
      "text": "in the Untied States only to find out..."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 30800.0,
      "end_time": 32260.0,
      "text": "you know...that...that it's not."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 32259.999999999996,
      "end_time": 33360.0,
      "text": "Okay, so if you are an American"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 33360.0,
      "end_time": 36040.0,
      "text": "this is how likely you are to die of various causes."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 36040.0,
      "end_time": 37900.0,
      "text": "You see violence down there at the bottom right corner."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 37900.0,
      "end_time": 39480.0,
      "text": "That's all interpersonal violence"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 39480.0,
      "end_time": 41540.0,
      "text": "war, terrorism, murder, etc."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 41540.0,
      "end_time": 43420.0,
      "text": "Now, because its victims are disproportionately young,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 43420.0,
      "end_time": 44880.0,
      "text": "violence becomes a bigger problem"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 44880.0,
      "end_time": 46880.0,
      "text": "if you change this visualization to"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 46880.0,
      "end_time": 48720.0,
      "text": "measure disability adjusted life years."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 48720.0,
      "end_time": 50180.0,
      "text": "Which is like a measure of how many years"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 50180.0,
      "end_time": 52560.0,
      "text": "of healthy life are lost due to various causes."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 52560.0,
      "end_time": 54740.0,
      "text": "But it's still a relatively small public health problem"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 54740.0,
      "end_time": 56140.0,
      "text": "in the United States. Smaller than"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 56140.0,
      "end_time": 58500.0,
      "text": "suicide, or drug overdoses, or asthma,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 58500.0,
      "end_time": 60500.0,
      "text": "or complications from preterm birth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 60500.0,
      "end_time": 61900.0,
      "text": "or traffic accidents."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 61900.0,
      "end_time": 63740.0,
      "text": "And also violence is shrinking faster"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 63740.0,
      "end_time": 65340.0,
      "text": "as a cause of death and disability"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 65340.0,
      "end_time": 66960.0,
      "text": "in the United States than any"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 66960.0,
      "end_time": 69240.0,
      "text": "other major cause except for HIV."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 69240.0,
      "end_time": 70880.0,
      "text": "So Hank, several studies have shown that on the Internet"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 70880.0,
      "end_time": 73820.0,
      "text": "we like to share what makes us outraged."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 73820.0,
      "end_time": 75740.0,
      "text": "And that incentivizes media companies, even"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 75740.0,
      "end_time": 77560.0,
      "text": "very small ones that make videos in their basements,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 77560.0,
      "end_time": 79200.0,
      "text": "to find outrageous stories because"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 79200.0,
      "end_time": 80640.0,
      "text": "we know that you will share them."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 80640.0,
      "end_time": 82720.0,
      "text": "I've done this. Like in 2010, I made a video about how"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 82720.0,
      "end_time": 85160.0,
      "text": "outrageous it is that we continue to mint pennies"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 85160.0,
      "end_time": 87100.0,
      "text": "even though they cost two cents a piece to make"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 87100.0,
      "end_time": 89300.0,
      "text": "and are never used to buy goods or services."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 89300.0,
      "end_time": 91420.0,
      "text": "The problem is the penny, while it's an obvious outrage,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 91420.0,
      "end_time": 93580.0,
      "text": "it's an exceedingly small outrage."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 93580.0,
      "end_time": 95520.0,
      "text": "I mean the US government could save far"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 95520.0,
      "end_time": 97400.0,
      "text": "more money by just by passing a long term"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 97400.0,
      "end_time": 99400.0,
      "text": "highway funding bill which Congress has been"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 99400.0,
      "end_time": 101440.0,
      "text": "unable to do for the last six years."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 101440.0,
      "end_time": 103500.0,
      "text": "But that isn't as narratively simple or as easy to get"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 103500.0,
      "end_time": 105860.0,
      "text": "outraged about, so we don't talk about it much."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 105860.0,
      "end_time": 108200.0,
      "text": "And then there is Martin Shkreli, the bond villainesque"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 108200.0,
      "end_time": 110200.0,
      "text": "former hedge fund manager, whose company"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 110200.0,
      "end_time": 111740.0,
      "text": "acquired the rights to a drug that"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 111740.0,
      "end_time": 113800.0,
      "text": "treats people with toxoplasmosis and"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 113800.0,
      "end_time": 117120.0,
      "text": "promptly rised the price from 13 dollars and 50 cents a pill"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 117120.0,
      "end_time": 119300.0,
      "text": "to 750 dollars a pill."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 119300.0,
      "end_time": 120920.0,
      "text": "The internet boiled with outrage until"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 120920.0,
      "end_time": 122700.0,
      "text": "the company promised to lower the price."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 122700.0,
      "end_time": 124580.0,
      "text": "Two months later, they've just announced, that for"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 124580.0,
      "end_time": 126600.0,
      "text": "some customers, they are going to lower that price"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 126600.0,
      "end_time": 129600.0,
      "text": "all the way down to 375 dollars a pill."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 129600.0,
      "end_time": 131760.0,
      "text": "But the outrage at this ass-hat masked a much"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 131760.0,
      "end_time": 133780.0,
      "text": "more complicated and interesting problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 133780.0,
      "end_time": 137840.0,
      "text": "Like, even before the price hike the drug cost 30 times more"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 137840.0,
      "end_time": 139780.0,
      "text": "in the US than it did in the UK."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 139780.0,
      "end_time": 142080.0,
      "text": "And these price hikes aren't even particularly new or rare."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 142080.0,
      "end_time": 144300.0,
      "text": "Longterm Nerdfighters will remember back in 2011"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 144300.0,
      "end_time": 146660.0,
      "text": "when Warner Chilcott raised the price of its drug"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 146660.0,
      "end_time": 149240.0,
      "text": "Asacol 1200 percent overnight."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 149240.0,
      "end_time": 150680.0,
      "text": "There are dozens of similar examples"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 150680.0,
      "end_time": 152240.0,
      "text": "and this stuff isn't happening because of"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 152240.0,
      "end_time": 154680.0,
      "text": "one individual's asshattery. It's happening because"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 154680.0,
      "end_time": 156440.0,
      "text": "there is a huge web of problems"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 156440.0,
      "end_time": 158580.0,
      "text": "with pharmaceutical markets in the US."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 158580.0,
      "end_time": 160580.0,
      "text": "Point being, our collective outrage may have"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 160580.0,
      "end_time": 163880.0,
      "text": "slightly decreased the price of one rarely prescribed drug."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 163880.0,
      "end_time": 166640.0,
      "text": "But it has done nothing to address the larger issues"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 166640.0,
      "end_time": 169140.0,
      "text": "that affect every American who takes medication."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 169140.0,
      "end_time": 171400.0,
      "text": "Now, of course, the Internet can and does grapple with"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 171400.0,
      "end_time": 173120.0,
      "text": "big and complicated problems and it's also"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 173120.0,
      "end_time": 175460.0,
      "text": "given a voice to people who traditionally have been"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 175460.0,
      "end_time": 177480.0,
      "text": "discriminated against in public discourse."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 177480.0,
      "end_time": 179640.0,
      "text": "And I also don't think there is anything wrong with being angry."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 179640.0,
      "end_time": 182120.0,
      "text": "Anger combined with sustained effort"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 182120.0,
      "end_time": 183900.0,
      "text": "can lead to real change."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 183900.0,
      "end_time": 185720.0,
      "text": "But when we allow ourselves to casually move from"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 185720.0,
      "end_time": 186940.0,
      "text": "one outrage to the next,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 186940.0,
      "end_time": 188500.0,
      "text": "from pennies to Martin Shkreli,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 188500.0,
      "end_time": 190460.0,
      "text": "nothing ever really changes."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 190460.0,
      "end_time": 192120.0,
      "text": "Well... Except that maybe we have become more afraid"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 192120.0,
      "end_time": 193200.0,
      "text": "and pessimistic."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 193200.0,
      "end_time": 195260.0,
      "text": "Like, since January of 2010, crime is down."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 195260.0,
      "end_time": 197620.0,
      "text": "The U.S. joblessness rate has fallen dramatically."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 197620.0,
      "end_time": 200660.0,
      "text": "The economy has grown and we report being happier"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 200660.0,
      "end_time": 202760.0,
      "text": "on average than we were five years ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 202760.0,
      "end_time": 205620.0,
      "text": "And yet every single month since January of 2010,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 205620.0,
      "end_time": 207920.0,
      "text": "more than two-thirds of Americans have felt"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 207920.0,
      "end_time": 210180.0,
      "text": "that the US is headed in the wrong direction."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 210180.0,
      "end_time": 212660.0,
      "text": "And I feel like we are unnecessarily inundated with bad news"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 212660.0,
      "end_time": 214720.0,
      "text": "because we seek it out and when we find it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 214720.0,
      "end_time": 216860.0,
      "text": "we share it. And so we become more afraid"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 216860.0,
      "end_time": 218900.0,
      "text": "and pessimistic than we need to be."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 218900.0,
      "end_time": 221160.0,
      "text": "But then again, as a nation we've never been healthier"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 221160.0,
      "end_time": 222720.0,
      "text": "or claim to be happier."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 222720.0,
      "end_time": 224920.0,
      "text": "So maybe we're getting exactly what we want."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 224920.0,
      "end_time": 226580.0,
      "text": "Even if we don't know it."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 226580.0,
      "end_time": 236580.0,
      "text": "Hank. I'll see you on Friday."
    }
  ]
}